Assurant Enters $350 Million, Four-Year Credit Deal With Banks

-- B y   M a r y e l l e n   T i g h e
-- 
2011-09-27T13:04:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-27/assurant-enters-350-million-four-year-credit-deal-with-banks.html
Assurant Inc. (AIZ) , the insurer of
foreclosed properties, entered a four-year, $350 million
revolving credit agreement with lenders including JPMorgan Chase
& Co. and Bank of America Corp.  The deal replaces a three-year, $350 million agreement that
was set to expire at the end of next year, the New York-based
insurer said today in a regulatory filing.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Maryellen Tighe in New York at 
 Mtighe6@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Kraut at   dkraut2@bloomberg.net  